<p class="ql-align-center">尼克尔 Z DX 16-50mm f/3.5-6.3 VR</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201021/86e9bf9126804b2dbfccb52e701d74a4.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">尼康官方样张</p>
